# Project Structure

This is a Laravel application for managing party RSVPs. Here are the key components:

## Core Components
- [app/Models/Rsvp.php](mdc:app/Models/Rsvp.php) - RSVP model for handling party attendance
- [app/Models/User.php](mdc:app/Models/User.php) - User model for attendee information
- [app/Models/Party.php](mdc:app/Models/Party.php) - Party model for event details

## Tests
The test suite in [tests/Feature/RsvpTest.php](mdc:tests/Feature/RsvpTest.php) provides comprehensive coverage of RSVP functionality including:
- Form submission validation
- User creation and updates
- RSVP message handling
- Mailchimp integration for email updates
- SMS updates handling

## Key Features
- Multiple RSVP submissions update existing records
- Message history is preserved and appended
- Email and SMS notification opt-in
- Mailchimp integration for mailing list management
- Volunteer tracking
- Attendance counting
